eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.engine.processor.ranking.randomaccess

Class CategoricalValueFinder<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.engine.processor.ranking.randomaccess.CategoricalValueFinder<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key (identifier) of the object.
    V - The textual value (keywords) of this object at a particular attribute.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IValueFinder<K,V>

    public class CategoricalValueFinder<K,V>
extends Object
implements IValueFinder<K,V>
    Updates the in-memory lookup with CATEGORICAL values used in random access operations during rank aggregation. This method inserts the categorical (keyword set) attribute value found for a given object identifier (primary key) in a data source collection (DBMS table of REST API data).
